parameters:
Let us offer prayers to the goddesses of freedom, Lunnu and
Mahha.

I'm dating the older sister next door. God forgives
everything... Now let's pray...

Worship is on Wednesdays and Sundays. We are always waiting
for you.

I also want to get married soon, but since I don't have a
partner, I thought I'd start with a prayer to the gods.

In the past, this area was a country where discrimination
was rampant. But two heroes who couldn't bear to see it
happen started a revolution. And that's how the current
Ulyssean was born.

This church was built as a symbol of that... It's not just
important to believe in God. We, too, need the commandments
to prevent us from repeating mistakes.
I hope that when I grow up, I can marry Yobiko-chan...!

Religious teachings often embody rationality. When you
adhere to them, you naturally learn how to survive in this
region. There are also reasons why they have been passed
down for a long time.

I don't believe in gods or anything like that, but I am
studying aspects of religion.

Ah, Lunaroa-chan... I want to spend another moment with
you...
